Class View

All Implemented Interfaces:
java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible, javax.swing.RootPaneContainer, javax.swing.WindowConstants
public class View
extends javax.swing.JFrame

This class represents the general user interface for the mission control application. It should be noted that *all* elements native to this class (native as in: declared in it) are positioned not with help of a layout manager, but instead absolutely via constant values. This should enable easy altering of the class in the future, even by persons other than the initial author.

Author:
Patrick Rutter
